</style><p>郡道さんは6月21日23時に卒業配信を行われ、所属する にじさんじを卒業。なお、YouTube公式チャンネルの配信アーカイブなどは既に非公開となっております。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="CahqSQ7bQA"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/a-person-who-is-believed-to-be-the-former-performer-and-voice-model-of-vtuber-gundo-mirei-has-started-activities-under-the-name-of-dokugai-chinami/">VTuber 郡道美玲の元演者／ボイスモデルとされる人物「毒ヶ衣ちなみ」の名前で活動へ</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;VTuber 郡道美玲の元演者／ボイスモデルとされる人物「毒ヶ衣ちなみ」の名前で活動へ&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/a-person-who-is-believed-to-be-the-former-performer-and-voice-model-of-vtuber-gundo-mirei-has-started-activities-under-the-name-of-dokugai-chinami/embed/#?secret=SmHJ3ofFd9#?secret=CahqSQ7bQA" data-secret="CahqSQ7bQA" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="g701IqJE6n"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-will-graduate-from-nijisanji-on-june-21/">VTuber 郡道美玲 6月21日をもってにじさんじを卒業</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;VTuber 郡道美玲 6月21日をもってにじさんじを卒業&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-will-graduate-from-nijisanji-on-june-21/embed/#?secret=7wCyedXBKT#?secret=g701IqJE6n" data-secret="g701IqJE6n" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="JiSftbTehN"> <a href="https://p2y